# Turing machine to recognize the following language:
#  L = {w | w is palindrome}
# White is represented as .
q0 q1 q2              # States
a b                   # String alphabet
a b .                 # Tape alphabet
q0                    # Initial state
q1                    # Accepting states
2                     # Number of tapes
# Transitions. Format:
# {state} {list of inputs} {destination state} {list of outpus} {list of movements}
q0 a . q0 a R a R
q0 b . q0 b R b R
q0 . . q1 . L . L
q1 a a q1 a L a S
q1 b b q1 b L b S
q1 a b q1 a L b S
q1 b a q1 b L a S
q1 . a q2 . R a S
q1 . b q2 . R b S
q2 a a q2 a R a L
q2 b b q2 b R b L
q2 . . q1 . S . S